:136050,"uid":52703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T19:45:39.000Z","msg":"果果都係因為錢入去做，又唔知自己賣啲產品同每個人個身體去衡量，仲睇埋啲唔知乜嘢博士扮晒專家，重點係佢哋多數都唔係註冊營養師，一味話減到肥就叫你食，你係減到人哋肥，但係整壞左人哋身子自己都唔知，成班懵撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f66a4b5333b34e1c283d9f4bcdfd3148fabc4364","tid":136050,"uid":52703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T04:40:12.000Z","msg":"有冇方法執左佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"561209df4f993fca4890e455dbfd12ba33c7f93e","tid":136050,"uid":52703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T10:30:01.000Z","msg":"成間野都有問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a938abe9832ea6f29b1820cebfcd5c21bf74a3b","tid":136050,"uid":72621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T04:48:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>成間野都有問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\namway d fd"},{"pid":"7537817c0e0f931de170e5607a55efe683f2256d","tid":136050,"uid":52703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T05:31:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>成間野都有問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\namway d fd</blockquote><br />\n好人好者唔洗sell都有人買"},{"pid":"97d4548de65c06675dab92690f6f0b729889e6da","tid":136050,"uid":2141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T22:44:24.000Z","msg":"見啲fd一飲就會做埋 係咁sell"},{"pid":"eafa2c32ab8c685099da6b7d1976728efe738447","tid":136050,"uid":52703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T05:18:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>見啲fd一飲就會做埋 係咁sell</blockquote><br />\n我有時睇見都唔高興，啲人又唔係專業人士就開粉呀整餐單呀，到有事真係自食其果"},{"pid":"d16763